WEBVTT

00:00:29.728 --> 00:00:34.427
that trying to understand the darkness
is something that's fascinated humans

00:00:34.451 --> 00:00:36.625
for thousands of years, maybe forever.

00:00:37.389 --> 00:00:39.246
And we know this

00:00:39.270 --> 00:00:44.007
because we find their ancient relics
of their attempts to map the sky.

00:00:46.317 --> 00:00:49.626
This tusk is over 30,000 years old.

00:00:50.413 --> 00:00:53.404
Some people think
that it's a carving of Orion

00:00:53.428 --> 00:00:55.515
or maybe a calendar.

00:00:55.944 --> 00:00:57.094
We don't know.

00:00:57.958 --> 00:01:02.156
The Fuxi star map is over 6,000 years old,